TITLE: Implement Client-Side Chat UI with AI SDK React `useChat` Hook
DESCRIPTION: This React component demonstrates how to integrate the `@ai-sdk/react` `useChat` hook to build a chat interface. It connects to the `/api/chat` endpoint, manages conversation history, and handles user input, including setting `maxSteps` for tool call processing.

