TITLE: Wire Up Chat UI with AI SDK Vue `useChat` Hook
DESCRIPTION: This Vue component (`pages/index.vue`) integrates the AI SDK's `Chat` component to manage and display chat messages. It uses a local `ref` for the input field, handles form submission to send messages via `chat.sendMessage`, and iterates through `chat.messages` to render the conversation history, distinguishing between user and AI roles and displaying message parts.

SOURCE: https://github.com/vercel/ai/blob/main/content/docs/02-getting-started/05-nuxt.mdx#_snippet_7

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
