TITLE: Migrate useChat roundtrip settings to maxSteps
DESCRIPTION: The `experimental_maxAutomaticRoundtrips`, `maxAutomaticRoundtrips`, and `maxToolRoundtrips` options have been removed from the `useChat` hook. Developers should now use the `maxSteps` option, where its value is equivalent to the previous roundtrips plus one.

SOURCE: https://github.com/vercel/ai/blob/v5/content/docs/08-migration-guides/29-migration-guide-4-0.mdx#_snippet_37

LANGUAGE: ts
CODE:
```
const { messages } = useChat({
  experimental_maxAutomaticRoundtrips: 2,
  // or maxAutomaticRoundtrips
  // or maxToolRoundtrips
  // ...
});
```

LANGUAGE: ts
CODE:
```
const { messages } = useChat({
  maxSteps: 3, // 2 roundtrips + 1
  // ...
});
```

