TITLE: Migrate experimental_resume to resumeStream in useChat
DESCRIPTION: The functionality to resume interrupted chat streams has been moved from the experimental `experimental_resume` option to the stable `resumeStream` property within the `useChat` hook. This change standardizes stream resumption.

SOURCE: https://github.com/vercel/ai/blob/main/content/docs/08-migration-guides/26-migration-guide-5-0.mdx#_snippet_34

LANGUAGE: TypeScript
CODE:
```
// Resume was experimental
const { messages } = useChat({
  experimental_resume: true,
});
```

LANGUAGE: TypeScript
CODE:
```
const { messages } = useChat({
  resumeStream: true, // Resume interrupted streams
});
```

