TITLE: AI SDK Tool Call Capabilities: Parallel Tool Calls
DESCRIPTION: This section outlines the support for parallel tool calls across different AI SDK environments. It distinguishes how AI SDK RSC (React Server Components) handles parallel calls versus the built-in support provided by the `useChat` hook in AI SDK UI.

SOURCE: https://github.com/vercel/ai/blob/v5/content/docs/05-ai-sdk-rsc/10-migrating-to-ui.mdx#_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: APIDOC
CODE:
```
AI SDK RSC:
  - streamUI does not support parallel tool calls.
  - Requires combination of streamText, createStreamableUI, and createStreamableValue.
AI SDK UI (useChat):
  - Built-in support for parallel tool calls.
  - Define multiple tools in streamText.
  - useChat handles parallel tool calls automatically.
```

